review_blob: I very enjoyable beer. Starts off sweet but still has a that great bitter IPA flavor. For a beer that has a 10.4% abv it is very smooth. If it werent a limited release could be the go to Imperial IPA for me
beer_name: Avery The Maharaja Imperial India Pale Ale

review_blob: A very intresting spin of their fancy lawnmower. Their is a nice citrus flavor to it but still has a nice crisp finish.
